snippet.description:

https://open.spotify.com/track/4f7QJX2A3SK4aVSK9bh4r5?si=9BkOo1axSHumBv-Jo3-BqA

Dalszerző: Tóth Andi
Szöveg: Tóth Andi, Belano
Producer/Mix/Master: Somogyvári Dani

Rendező: Rádli Bence, Tóth Andi
Operatőr: Rádli Bence
1st AC: Farkas Dávid
Fővilágosító: Schäffer Gábor
Produkciós asszisztens: Nagy Lászlo
Vágó / Colorist: Rádli Bence
Gyártásvezető: Tóth István (Bellator Records)
Koreográfus: Pauker Barbara
Táncosok: Jávori Lili, Némethy Viktória, Mihály Zsófia, Pauker Barbara, Pálinkás Ádám, Tatai Kristóf, Szarka Norbert, Köpösdi Ádám
Werk fotó: Kovács Bálint
Werk videó: Jámbor Erik

Külön köszönet a BiotechUSA-nak, hogy biztosították a táncosok ruháját. 

Management / Marketing:
Tóth István / Bellator Management
+36703268432 / marketing@bellatormanagement.hu

Dalszöveg:

(Andi)
Fug de el dar nu mă lasă
Mă aruncă sus pe masă
Tot îl rog dar nu pleacă
Dar nici nu vreau
Doar lângă tine stau
 
(Belano)
Fug de ea el rohanok, szaladok tőled el
Bele se szólok, jönnek a csajok
Felkínálják magukat, kösz de nem
Was geht ab man 
Nem tudom, hogy mire van a gádzsi nagyba hah
Keresem egy másik csajban
Ez zsákbamacska
De bárcsak abbahagynád
No Belano ist online 
Nem túlzok, téged kérlek all night
Néha más korosztálynak is bejön a Belano style
Lass das bebe ja 
Használj ki, gyere rám
Megrontott, én húzom a derekát magamhoz közel
A szívem nézettséget generál
 
(Andi)
Fug de el dar nu mă lasă
Mă aruncă sus pe masă
Tot îl rog dar nu pleacă
Dar nici nu vreau
Doar lângă tine stau
 
(Belano)
Szexi a gádzsi dar nu o vreau
Echte beweise im irheim urlaub
Bebe aber gehe nicht kaputt
Mentem a szívem, a lelkem ott hagyom
Felváglak az asztalra, 
Nem érdekel, mit mondanak mások
Senki sem vigasztalhat meg
Hiába vannak csinos lányok
Babe, babe
Azt akarom, hogy az enyém legyél
Még, még
Tagadom, belehalok 
Egyre nagyobb a tét
Wey, wey
Ez a gádzsi egy főnyeremény
Már megint róla szól a zeném,
Csak az enyém
Héj
 
(Andi)
Fug de el dar nu mă lasă
Mă aruncă sus pe masă
Tot îl rog dar nu pleacă
Dar nici nu vreau
Doar lângă tine stau
 
Repede hey
Zii că mă vrei
Mindenki rólad álmodik
 
Atinge-mă, hai
Dă-mi tot ce ai
Dă-mi un grrr
Dă-mi un tu tata tu tu ta
tu ta ta tu tu ta
Iubirea mea
 
Fut utánam kiabálva
Azt hiszi féltenie kell.
Óv a karjaiba zárva
Ahogy rám néz, remegek
 
Tre’ să te-ntreb, ai avut vreodată
treabă cu o gagică ardeleancă?
 
Jelele lele lelelele
 
Fug de el dar nu mă lasă
Mă aruncă sus pe masă
Tot îl rog dar nu pleacă
Dar nici nu vreau
Doar lângă tine stau

snippet.title: I Got Hunted By the Minecraft LAW
snippet.description:
im innocent dawg (aside from those 1000 players)

I Got Hunted By the Minecraft LAW

minor spoilers below

featuring: @Spokeishere @4CVIT @minutetechmc @PrinceZam @MapiccMc @Leowook @JadenMAN 

music from:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9UKPs9ZisfhMJdalnETLRg (tons of the music I use is by AZALI so check him out!) 
https://www.youtube.com/@andreaszoeller (all of the minecraft OST remixes are by him!)
https://www.youtube.com/@DMDOKURO (evil void song when spoke shows up..)

This is a Minecraft video recorded in the Unstable Universe / Unstable SMP that is staged for story-telling purposes; any more staged videos I upload will have a disclaimer in the description saying that they are also staged. Also, a lot of the game mechanics/glitches/redstone discussed in Unstable SMP videos are unique to the Unstable SMP / Unstable Universe and either will not work the same/do not exist in vanilla Minecraft. 

music also from: official minecraft soundtrack, official elder scrolls soundtracks, official enderal soundtrack, epidemic sound (https://www.epidemicsound.com), storyblocks (https://www.storyblocks.com), artlist (https://artlist.io), soundstripe (https://www.soundstripe.com), fesliyan studios (https://www.fesliyanstudios.com/royalty-free-music), and envato (https://elements.envato.com/)

Enderal Soundtrack (HQ): Bone Hunter - Knochenjäger https://youtu.be/LchGhXSXxZk by Marvin Kopp, licensed under CC BY 4.0 https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

Enderal Soundtrack - Extended (HQ): Run of Things - Lauf der Dinge https://youtu.be/V5mExzEKWs8 by Marvin Kopp, licensed under CC BY 4.0 https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

snippet.title: Пацаны 5 сезон - разбор трейлера. Кого бьёт Хоумлендер и зачем ему нужен Солдатик?
snippet.description:
Кого избивает Хоумлендер? Кто умрёт в 5 сезоне «Пацанов»? Что задумала сестра Сейдж и зачем Солдатик нужен Джону? Вопросов много. Сегодня постараюсь ответить на все и задать другие. 4 сезон «Пацанов» разочаровал. Но трейлер 5 сезона — просто огонь. Похоже, финал истории обещает быть действительно эпичным.

snippet.title: Game Of Thrones | Season 9 (2027) | First Trailer
snippet.description:
#gameofthrones #got #trailer 
What if the story didn’t end at the Iron Throne?
This trailer imagines what a full Game of Thrones Season 9 could look like—built on the strongest fan theories, world-building details, and long-discussed lore that the show never explored. Every scene, voiceover, and moment in this trailer was crafted to feel grounded in the world George R.R. Martin created, while presenting a darker continuation of the story.

~STORY CONCEPT & THEORIES USED
1. Jon Snow’s Life Beyond the Wall
-After the events of Season 8, Jon travels deep into the true North. Fan theories suggest:
-A new icy threat awakens beyond the known lands
-The mysteries of the White Walkers were never truly resolved
-Jon becomes a leader among the Wildlings, facing a danger even greater than the Night King
This trailer explores a version of Jon forced back into battle—not for thrones, but for survival.

2. Daenerys Targaryen’s Resurrection
One of the most popular theories: Drogon did not fly west without purpose.
The show mentions a sighting near Volantis—the home of the Red Temple and the powerful Red Priestess Kinvara.
Just like Jon Snow and Beric Dondarrion, resurrection is possible through the Lord of Light.
In this concept, we explore:
-Drogon delivering Daenerys to the Red Priests
-A dangerous ritual with a heavy cost
-The return of a queen who is no longer the same

3. King Bran as the Hidden Villain
A dark fan theory suggests:
-Bran manipulated the events of Westeros to take the throne
-He may have used his powers to influence minds and outcomes
Some even claim Bran could be connected to the Night King’s creation
Season 9 in this concept asks:
What if the new king is not peace, but prophecy unfolding?

~Game of thrones season 9 cast:
-Kit Harington – Jon Snow
-Maisie Williams – Arya Stark
-Emilia Clarke – Daenerys Targaryen
-Peter Dinklage – Tyrion Lannister
-Isaac Hempstead Wright – Bran Stark
-Ania Bukstein – Kinvara (Red Priestess)
-Gwendoline Christie – Brienne of Tarth
-Liam Cunningham – Davos Seaworth
-Jacob Anderson – Grey Worm
And more returning characters imagined in a new conflict.

📅 Game Of Thrones Season 9 RELEASE DATE (Concept Only)
There is no official Season 9 in development at HBO.
This trailer is a fan-made creative project, made to visualize how the story could continue based on theories and lore.

📌 DISCLAIMER
This is a fan-made concept trailer.
It is not affiliated with HBO, George R.R. Martin, or the official Game of Thrones franchise.
This video is made purely for entertainment, storytelling, and appreciation of the series.
All rights to Game of Thrones belong to their respective owners.

🔥 If you enjoyed this concept…
LIKE, COMMENT your theories, and SUBSCRIBE for more fan-made trailers and cinematic projects.

'Winter may have ended…
but the story never truly did.'
